QuestData.Title: The Last Gasp of Y'Shaarj
QuestData.Description: A dark, vaporous substance stains the floor of the room. This is all that remains of the Old God Y'Shaarj.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Lorewalker Cho in the Siege of Orgrimmar.
